    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this exceptionally well-maintained vehicle, representing a superior balance of performance and long-term value. This unit has undergone a rigorous multi-point inspection to ensure it adheres to our exacting standards for mechanical reliability and aesthetic presentation. With a documented service history and a refined interior, it offers a sophisticated driving experience for the discerning owner. We invite you to acquire this distinguished example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 36800.0,
